1. For Approval remarks might include:
- "All marriage documents verified and authentic"
- "Both parties' consent verified"
- "Age requirements met for both parties"
- "No legal impediments found"
- "Witness statements verified"
- "Religious ceremony documentation complete"
- "Marriage registration requirements fulfilled"

2. For Rejection remarks might include:
- "Incomplete documentation from one or both parties"
- "Age requirement not met"
- "Missing witness information"
- "Discrepancy in submitted documents"
- "Legal impediment discovered"
- "Required waiting period not observed"
- "Missing proof of divorce/widowhood (if applicable)"
- "Invalid identification documents"
- "Missing parental consent (if required)"